rComments: Such a great professor. Clarify everything so clearly in lectures. Humorous and the lecture is engaging. You will never regret enrolling in his class. Really care about students. Since he was once the student of U of T, he knows what we are caring about :-)
Great prof who makes great lectures with very detailed slides. Very enjoyable to be in his class, makes great jokes and cares about his students.
He really cares about his students!

Hamid is a great prof. He talks about himself in the third person, which is a bit weird, but he is a funny guy. I found his lectures really engaging; he did his best to not just read off of the PowerPoint slides. His tests were sometimes a bit confusing, but he did give students bonus marks when the midterm average was low.
